Looks super delicious!😍share the recipe pls!!

Damn I’m happy I found the most perfect pizza🍕 crust recipe...EVER! And it doesn’t even require an oven.

I just need flour, baking powder, yogurt... and pan fry it using the same @cookyn.inc recipe the kids used during their online cooking class.

And, thankfully, the kids remembered it, so they could make and knead the dough for me.

I just can’t handle how fluffehhhhhh and soft and fresh the pizza crust is! There honestly is not much point in buying pizzas (always so 💰 when it’s such basic ingredients duh) anymore.

@ericayeo Probably! very basic recipe so Cookyn could walk the kids through it online. I had to cook it for them on the stove though. Btw, if you cover it the cheese will melt, so no need to put into the oven right?
Pretty sure we just used the same pizza dough recipe at my gf’s place earlier today. Heh. We did pop it into the oven to finish off though.
Looks super delicious!😍share the recipe pls!!
